 *   public/avatars/wolf.jpg, dragon.jpg, castle.jpg, grave.jpg, skull.jpg
 *
 * UI always prefers the image at `src`; emoji is only an onError fallback
 * if a file fails to load. `avatar_key` stores the filename.
 */

